</h1>

<div class=3D"calculator_info">
    Calculates how much priming sugar to add at bottling time for home brew=
ed beer. Includes the residual amount of CO<sub>2</sub> present in the beer=
 due to fermentation. Works for Corn Sugar (Dextrose), Table Sugar (Sucrose=
),  Dry Malt Extract (DME), and variety of priming sugars. Also known as bo=
ttle priming. Sugar is added at bottling time. The remaining yeast ferment =
the sugar and this produces CO<sub>2</sub>.
